				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$t_d$$\end{document}td. Processes that are not part of the decision-making process (e.g., encoding the stimuli and executing a motor response) are captured in the non-decision time parameter \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
